name: Guardian
description:
BECOME A YESHIN NORBU GUARDIAN

rnAnother way to Support the center is by becoming a Yeshin Norbu Guardian. This is for everyone who cares a little extra about Yeshin Norbu’s long term financial stability and growth, through giving a regular support to the centre, either monthly, quarterly or yearly.rnrnAll Yeshin Norbu Guardians will receive a Yeshin Norbu friends bag as a symbol of our gratitude and receive first hand notifications when there are special events taking place at the centre.
